WEBVTT

00:00.010 --> 00:01.300
Previously on One Tree Hill...

00:01.310 --> 00:04.100
You are heading down a dangerous pass.

00:04.310 --> 00:05.500
You don't have a job.

00:05.568 --> 00:06.468
Your honor...

00:06.536 --> 00:07.936
She does have a job.

00:08.003 --> 00:09.671
She works for me.

00:09.739 --> 00:11.372
How did we get the
funding for the movie?

00:11.508 --> 00:14.739
My father and I put up the
money, because I believe in you.

00:14.807 --> 00:16.998
All day long I've been
trying to figure out

00:17.066 --> 00:19.974
how to get past the
you-and-Alex thing.

00:20.042 --> 00:21.816
Maybe right now, you
need to work on you,

00:21.883 --> 00:23.547
and I need to work on me.

00:24.114 --> 00:25.525
Goodbye, Brooke.

00:25.593 --> 00:26.789
Hey, Tay.

00:27.090 --> 00:29.290
